    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Family containing around 30 genera and 350 species of flowering plants. It originated in Africa, although this is not the center of its extant diversity; representatives are found in most tropical areas of the world except Australia.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
